{"tid":703023,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"無人係唱唔到歌既 解答新手唱歌上既疑問","createTime":"2018-06-15T11:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T02:35:56.000Z","uid":153939,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"72c28ae3a649bee9fbfd2e05783b3c0fa73d7e78","tid":703023,"uid":153939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"講真 我以前唱歌都係同好多人一樣 成日走音 音色好唔穩 唱幾首歌喉嚨就會好緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係經過有系統既訓練 終於明白 唱歌其實同做gym 做其他運動一樣 係可以慢慢訓練既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 需要知道既其實係一個方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n方法並唔係不斷不斷地唱歌去令自己進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有系統既訓練方法其實係包括<br />\n-用diaphragm（肚仔呼吸大法）<br />\n<br />\n唱歌所有所有既力量 不論高低音都要用肚嚟support 肚仔就等於一部車既engine <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不論你低音定高音你唔開引擎部車係跑得唔遠 特別係上到高音 唔用肚仔係hold唔住既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-發聲練習<br />\n發聲練習可以令你聲帶做warm up同做運動一樣可以防止受傷 又可以幫你練音息穩定度 練open throat張咀巴口腔內部打開 令唱歌更輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fa1e52af3269f8866b73523277a8c52bfd466d","tid":703023,"uid":153939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:54:15.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88991c577f829974b4153a7996625c1b9fee1cc","tid":703023,"uid":46645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:13:48.000Z","msg":"唱首黎聽下"},{"pid":"782769064f07db18571d91b8af4cd8833e700833","tid":703023,"uid":153939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c88991c577f829974b4153a7996625c1b9fee1cc","tid":703023,"uid":46645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited