1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=79318e9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HenryCcc</a>"},{"pid":"66dff46d537e789b741ed3ddf9ccbf360dd4b2a8","tid":703023,"uid":156618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:33:26.000Z","msg":"留名，五音不全小六之後就冇唱過歌，但最近好想學唱歌，唱偶像啲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3409f389313ef99a1685684278b79b3c471bf6c","tid":703023,"uid":153939,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66dff46d537e789b741ed3ddf9ccbf360dd4b2a8","tid":703023,"uid":156618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:33:26.000Z","msg":"留名，五音不全小六之後就冇唱過歌，但最近好想學唱歌，唱偶像啲歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"巴打想唱邊位偶像既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4ea79dcae0d7ea33d0408c8af3a71d07a18f8b","tid":703023,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:42:39.000Z","msg":"好似馮文樂嗰啲扮聲唱歌有冇得練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"483dbd5edbbfa9c95db3e76cd69ef6b5a70320f0","tid":703023,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"把聲唔入咪可以點？？<br />\n同埋點練高音，高少少key都上唔到去"},{"pid":"ca004886bf14e902a5b0b0cd20f074abbadb4f86","tid":703023,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e20d6f2d1a73f539774df57fb02674dd5bffc2a0","tid":703023,"uid":153939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e4ea79dcae0d7ea33d0408c8af3a71d07a18f8b","tid":703023,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018